 Si(3C-SiC) LEIP LAB  EVAL-SEP17 Y. Zhu, J.L. Wormald, A.I. Hawari  43 1451     
 REF. 2 (2014)        DIST-FEB18                                    43 1451     
----ENDF/B-VIII.0     MATERIAL 43                                   43 1451     
-----THERMAL NEUTRON SCATTERING DATA                                43 1451     
------ENDF-6 FORMAT                                                 43 1451     
                                                                    43 1451     
 Temperatures = 300, 400, 500, 600, 700, 800, 1000, 1200 K          43 1451     
                                                                    43 1451     
 History                                                            43 1451     
 -------                                                            43 1451     
                                                                    43 1451     
 This library was produced by the Low Energy Interaction Physics    43 1451     
 (LEIP) group at NC State University.  The inelastic scattering     43 1451     
 cross section libraries for 3C-SiC were fully developed using      43 1451     
 ab-initio and lattice dynamics methods [1].  Phonon properties of  43 1451     
 3C-SiC are estimated using ab-initio calculated forces inside the  43 1451     
 lattice [2]. Eight temperatures are available in this library.     43 1451     
 The LEAPR module from NJOY code system was used to produce File 7  43 1451     
 MT = 2, 4 data for SiC as a mixed moderator.  Modifications to     43 1451     
 the LEAPR source code were made to calculate the coherent elastic  43 1451     
 cross section for 3C-SiC [2,3].  By convention, MAT=43 and ZA=143  43 1451     
 are used for Si in 3C-SiC.                                         43 1451     
                                                                    43 1451     
 References                                                         43 1451     
 ----------                                                         43 1451     
                                                                    43 1451     
 1. A.I. Hawari, "Modern Techniques in Inelastic Thermal Neutron    43 1451     
    Scattering Analysis," Nuclear Data Sheets 118 (2014) 172.       43 1451     
 2. Y. Zhu, "Thermal Neutron Scattering Cross Sections for Silicon  43 1451     
    Carbide", MS thesis, North Carolina State University (2014).    43 1451     
 3. Y. Zhu, A. Hawari, "Implementation of a Generalized Coherent    43 1451     
    Elastic Scattering Formulation for Thermal Neutron Scattering   43 1451     
    Analysis", Proceedings of International Conference on Nuclear   43 1451     
    Criticality Safety, Charlotte, NC, September 13-17, 2015.       43 1451     
